version_description: * Minor bug fixes with iCloud Drive and Dropbox

* Now able to generate video reports with overlays for dynamic wireframe, dashboard measurements and snapshots.
* Minor bug fixes
Fixed bug when clicking outside of a video while locating dots.
Fixed a bug with dot tracking introduced in version 1.1.1.

* Support for iOS 11 and iPhone X
* Improved dot tracking algorithm
* Reduced memory load when generating video with overlays

* Support page for introduction video and FAQ.
* Added Ankle Angle.
* Minor bug fixes.
